    <section id="NiFi+Project+Incubation+Status">
      <title>NiFi Project Incubation Status</title>
      <p>This page tracks the project status, incubator-wise. For more general
         project status, look on the project website.</p>
      <p>The Apache NiFi project graduated as a TLP on July 15th 2015</p>
      <p><span class='graduated'>The NiFi project graduated on 2015-07-15</span></p>
    </section>
    <section id="Description">
      <title>Description</title>
      <p>Apache NiFi is an easy to use, powerful, and reliable system to process and distribute data.</p>
    </section>
